Privacy Policy — CineMat Generator
Last updated: March 13, 2026
CineMat Generator does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data or user information of any kind.
No data collection. CineMat Generator does not collect any information about you or your device.
No analytics. The app contains no analytics frameworks, crash reporters, or usage tracking of any kind.
No network activity. CineMat Generator never connects to the internet. All image processing and export functions happen entirely on your device.
No third-party SDKs. The app contains no third-party code that could collect data on our behalf.
Your images stay on your device. Any frame grabs you load into CineMat Generator are processed locally and never leave your device.
No accounts required. CineMat Generator requires no login, registration, or account of any kind.

Contact
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, open an issue at github.com/yourusername/cinemat-generator or contact us through the App Store support link.

This policy applies to CineMat Generator for macOS, iOS, and iPadOS.
